<p>
  Curated, multi-sensor dataset for glacial lake detection and segmentation. Includes Sentinel-1 (VV, VH),
  Sentinel-2 (Blue, Green, Red, NIR, SWIR-11, SWIR-12), NDWI, DEM, and slope. Designed for training and
  benchmarking geo-foundational and segmentation models.
</p>
